# 37b830e248a04c35b3ed94f58178126a
#: ../../source/training/tot/501_adult_learning.rst:227
msgid ""
"Adults like an atmosphere of learning that promotes self-confidence. This is "
"related to their desire to be respected. Start with simple things to "
"increase their confidence."
msgstr ""
"Orang dewasa menyukai suasana pembelajaran yang membangkitkan kepercayaan "
"diri. Hal ini berkaitan dengan keinginan untuk dihargai. Mulailah "
"pembelajaran dengan hal-hal yang mudah sehingga kepercayaan diri mereka "
"meningkat."

# 2524c992c5a248828b313110b37fd79d
#: ../../source/training/tot/501_adult_learning.rst:230
msgid ""
"Adults need longer time to learn as they need to validate new information. "
"When they receive information, they will validate it based on their "
"experience."
msgstr ""
"Orang dewasa memerlukan waktu yang lebih panjang dalam belajar karena perlu "
"memvalidasi informasi baru. Orang dewasa tidak sekedar menerima informasi "
"melainkan memvalidasi informasi berdasarkan pengalaman-pengalaman mereka."

# 445f5c5489624a56a028e1ebe341a84b
